     ] )
  ] ) ; # 
  fhir:description [ fhir:v "This implementation guide defines the FHIR logical models and terminology for the DHIS2 Cancer Registry metadata package, aligned with CanReg5 data standards developed by the International Agency for Research on Cancer (IARC). The FHIR artifacts in this IG are generated from a DHIS2 Tracker program for individual-level cancer case registration supporting population-based monitoring, with embedded data quality control checks based on CanReg5 validation logic covering age, sex, topography, morphology, behaviour, grade and basis of diagnosis combinations."] ; # 
